{"tid":2514062,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"ETH3000慶祝區+後市策略","createTime":"2021-05-03T04:20:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T05:06:35.000Z","uid":360741,"like":131,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"e5f415382b28a7ac6f71938b0d3ff647ea8a8fa0","tid":2514062,"uid":360741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T04:20:46.000Z","msg":"第一次出文叫大家買ETH既時候係$135一粒，今日已經過左$3000啦，成功找數。<br />\n<br />\n以太坊黎緊呢半年兩個重要升級，EIP1559同埋ETH 2.0鏈融合。生態系統上有各個Layer 2 project，全部進展都唔錯，我年尾有機會再升3倍。<br />\n<br />\n但係區塊鏈技術發展一日千里，變化實在太快，為左防止升級失敗/有bug/礦工反抗eip1559/延期/比競爭鏈追上等等既風險，我已經係$3000左右回左個本，仲鎖定左少少獲利，投入返股市。其他就有得佢放風箏，睇下有冇機會上到$5000-$10000，再分段獲利。<br />\n<br />\n仲未買入既可以買啲，但要提提大家，最低風險最好賺既價值發現(price discovery)階段已經過去，之後落黎既升幅係要睇技術發展，用風險換回報。<br />\n<br />\n有買到既，大家飲杯<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0e1c30fe58999a0e6b94f4559add32c2cdaec9c","tid":2514062,"uid":29836,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T04:21:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />thx"},{"pid":"882a93b6ec1c085f28482a0944276707be57357d","tid":2514062,"uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T04:21:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c38042ea16776e05b0523f2ca22fa5023b3ed781","tid":2514062,"uid":4050,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T04:21:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />留名"},{"pid":"a8bed423ec9e4ea0abedcc78ae50778b936a8163","tid":2514062,"uid":103618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T04:21:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.